00045  SUBROUTINE MemAlloc(FLAG)
00046 
00047 ! Common Variables
00048  USE Domain,     ONLY : ni, ni_f, xmax, xmax_f, xmin, xmin_f, ymax, ymax_f, ymin, ymin_f
00049  USE FluidParams
00050  USE LBMParams,  ONLY : f, fbar, fdim, g, gbar, gdim
00051  IMPLICIT NONE
00052 
00053 ! Input/Output Parameters
00054  INTEGER, INTENT (IN) :: FLAG
00055 
00056  IF(FLAG == 1) THEN
00057 
00058 ! Memory allocation for momentum/pressure grid arrays
00059  ALLOCATE(    p(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax) )
00060  ALLOCATE(  rho(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax) )
00061  ALLOCATE(    u(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax,1:2) )
00062  ALLOCATE(   ni(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax,1:4) )
00063  ALLOCATE(    g(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax,0:gdim) )
00064  ALLOCATE( gbar(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax,0:gdim) )
00065 
00066 ! Memory allocation for order parameter grid arrays
00067  ALLOCATE(   p_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00068  ALLOCATE( rho_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00069  ALLOCATE( psi_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00070  ALLOCATE(   u_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f,1:2) )
00071  ALLOCATE(  ni_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f,1:4) )
00072  ALLOCATE(     f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f,0:fdim) )
00073  ALLOCATE(  fbar(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f,0:fdim) )
00074 
00075 ! Memory allocation for differential terms in the momentum/pressure grid
00076  ALLOCATE(       GX(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax) )
00077  ALLOCATE(       GY(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax) )
00078  ALLOCATE( gradRhoX(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax) )
00079  ALLOCATE( gradRhoY(xmin:xmax,ymin:ymax) )
00080 
00081 ! Memory allocation for differential terms in the order parameter grid
00082  ALLOCATE(  gradRhoX_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00083  ALLOCATE(  gradRhoY_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00084  ALLOCATE( gradRhoSq_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00085  ALLOCATE( gradRhoXX_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00086  ALLOCATE( gradRhoXY_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00087  ALLOCATE( gradRhoYY_f(xmin_f:xmax_f,ymin_f:ymax_f) )
00088 
00089  ELSE
00090 
00091 ! Free memory
00092  DEALLOCATE( p )
00093  DEALLOCATE( u )
00094  DEALLOCATE( g )
00095  DEALLOCATE( ni )
00096  DEALLOCATE( rho )
00097  DEALLOCATE( gbar )
00098  DEALLOCATE( gradRhoX )
00099  DEALLOCATE( gradRhoY )
00100  DEALLOCATE( GX )
00101  DEALLOCATE( GY )
00102 
00103 
00104  DEALLOCATE( p_f )
00105  DEALLOCATE( u_f )
00106  DEALLOCATE( f )
00107  DEALLOCATE( ni_f )
00108  DEALLOCATE( rho_f )
00109  DEALLOCATE( psi_f )
00110  DEALLOCATE( fbar )
00111  DEALLOCATE( gradRhoX_f )
00112  DEALLOCATE( gradRhoY_f )
00113  DEALLOCATE( gradRhoSq_f )
00114  DEALLOCATE( gradRhoXX_f )
